https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/QPqLroIupocKoF8O0vjhkQhzLf.jpg An accoustic version of the first tour album of the French Quebecker singer Annie Villeneuve, filmed the 21 of October 2006, at Espace Dell'Arte in Montreal. This version also contains a documentary on the backstage production of the tour, as well as commentary by Annie, her twin sister Suzie and the musicians of the tour.
